name: load
description: Loads a module, if it fails while loading, it will spit an error as a txt file

name: reload
description: Reoads a module, if it fails while reloading, it will spit an error as a txt file

name: unload
description: Unloads a module, if it fails while loading, it will spit an error as a txt file

name: help
description: Sends dedicated help for a specific command, if no command is specified, it will send a list of all commands

parameters.name: command
parameters.description: The command to get help for

name: info
description:
Sends information about the bot, this includes:
Total Guilds, Total Members, Bot Version, Python Version and Bot Uptime

name: invite
brief: Sends an invite link for the bot and the bot's support server
description: Sends an invite link for the bot and the bot's support server

name: ping
description: Sends the bots latency, which is the latency between a HEARTBEAT and a HEARTBEAT_ACK in miliseconds
